rd.dev.simulation.datamanagement

Class SelectionsProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • rd.dev.simulation.datamanagement.DataManager
      • rd.dev.simulation.datamanagement.SelectionsProvider

  • public class SelectionsProvider
extends DataManager
    this class is a specialized extension of DataManager which provides access to the timeStamp and project entities. These are separated out for convenience; there is no special reason other than conciseness and ease of access to the code
